caption:
A tomografia computadorizada pode ser problemática às vezes, mas a preservação irreal do lagarto – tanto quanto as pálpebras duplas do olho esquerdo ainda estão lá – ajudou os pesquisadores a transformar as varreduras em representações assustadoramente realistas de uma criatura que não anda na Terra desde meados de -Cretáceo. Seus órgãos podem não ter conseguido, mas a traqueia e os brônquios foram preservados. Observando mais de perto o esqueleto e os padrões das escamas, eles conseguiram perceber que ainda não estava maduro.

Este pequeno lagarto pode ter enormes implicações sobre como seus sucessores acabaram onde estão agora. Comparações morfológicas foram usadas para encontrar seus parentes sobreviventes mais próximos, bem como análise filogenética, que descobre conexões evolutivas através da morfologia de espécies extintas e existentes e dados moleculares de espécies existentes. O que os pesquisadores descobriram ao examinar mais de perto o espécime foi que é um scincoid (o que significa que se assemelha a um skink ) que ecoa as características de alguns xantusiids , que são endêmicos da América do Norte. Então, como o fóssil foi parar em Mianmar? É possível que o Rhetinosaurus tenha gerado em outro lugar quando seu território se mudou para outro lugar.

“Isso é complicado, porque existem outras hipóteses sobre a origem e a paleoposição da microplaca Burma Terrane”, disse Čerňanský. “Ainda é bastante controverso e deixa espaço para outras interpretações sobre a origem das linhagens de animais que ocorrem lá durante o Cretáceo.”

Acredita-se que os Xantusiids, ou lagartos noturnos , tenham divergido dos cordyloformes , lagartos fortemente blindados que surgiram pela primeira vez na África, em algum momento durante o Jurássico. Se o Retinossauro é realmente um ancestral dos xantusiídeos americanos, ou lagartos noturnos.

caption:
#naturalnosc #kobiecosc to ona 🤍@nostressbeauty 🤍 
Uwielbiam 
・・・
Warsztaty #glowmakeup & #contouring @makeupwiedenski odwiedziłam już drugi raz. #kamilawiedenskamakeup wymaga, aby na warsztaty przynieść kosmetyki, których aktualnie się używa, pojawić się w makijażu (jednak ze świadomością, że zostanie usunięty), albo sauté i zostawić stare, codzienne nawyki za drzwiami. Każda z nas maluje się na co dzień trochę na pamięć. I to jest ok, ale czasem prostym trickiem, przy niewielkim nakładzie sił można uzyskać efekt promiennej skóry, pełniejszych ust czy młodszego oka. Aby cera była taka, jak na zdjęciu, należy wklepywać palcami korektor, podkład i rozświetlacz, popracować nad każdym elementem makijażu, żeby go zblendować i aby wyglądał jak skóra a nie żywa reklama produktów do makijażu (osobno widoczny puder, róż czy korektor). Dziś pracowałyśmy nad konturem twarzy. U każdej z uczestniczek warsztatów - nieco inne miejsca wymagały aplikacji bronzera, a inne pudru czy rozświetlacza. Ja dowiedziałam się jak prawidłowo używać korektora, żeby wyglądać na wypoczętą, jak aplikować róż żeby zadziałał jak optyczny lifting i czego nie robić, by nie dodawać sobie lat. Polecam takie warsztaty. To jedna z tych form kobiecych kręgów, które uwielbiam, bo naprawdę dużo z nich wynoszę. Tymi samymi kosmetykami można wyczarować coś zupełnie innego. Wystarczy znać odrobinę techniki. I jak już wspomniałam: wyjść z codziennych schematów. Używać mniej warstw, stosować jeden produkt do wielu różnych zadań. I ze zwykłego makijażu dziennego powstaje genialny efekt:) dziś bardzo podobało mi się też działanie w podgrupach. Miałyśmy powiedzieć jaki jest największy atut twarzy koleżanki, która siedzi obok i co powinna podkreślać. Miło nie zaczynać rozmowy od krytyki, która wychodzi nam znacznie łatwiej, nie klepać o „niedoskonałościach”, tylko o zapomnianych przez nas zaletach. Jeśli macie siostrę, przyjaciółkę czy mamę, weźcie ją na takie spotkanie. Piękna sprawa (i świetny prezent tak przy okazji)! #nostressbeauty #selfie #warsztaty #makijaż #makeup #makeuptutorial #with #makeupartist

caption:
The most Embarrassing health problem ➡️ Gynecomestia

Gynaecomastia is the enlargement of the breast in mens, It is important to how to Detect Gynaecomastia so that it can be prevented on time. 

In many cases it does not disappear on their own therefore early detection will enable the sufferer to seek help..

Gynaecomastia includes growth of a small lumps under the nipple region commonly linked with some pain and softness or hardness of area. Once the symptom shows up, it is advisable to consult a skin doctor for proper medical diagnosis.

The visible signs of Gynecomastia are-

lumps under the nipple region, the breast developed  abnormally and also the breasts becomes soft. In chronic issues, the various grades of skin ulcer and sometimes nipple discharges may be seen. The enlargement of  disk-shaped tissue just beneath the nipple may be seen which is sometimes painful when touched.

Many people have a misunderstanding of having gyno when they are fat.. discomfort of this area often leads to itching..

A estrela desconhecida de Jurassic Park era um mosquito congelado em âmbar. Embora você não possa realmente extrair sangue de espécimes como esse, você pode ser transportado de volta no tempo se olhar para um espécime de seiva de árvore fossilizada e encontrar um lagarto de 110 milhões de anos olhando para você.

As criaturas ficam presas em âmbar o tempo todo, mas a maioria dos achados pré-históricos são insetos. O âmbar é um ótimo material para a preservação de artrópodes por causa de suas conchas já duras que aguentam mesmo se o interior se desintegrar. Mas e um lagarto? Retinosaurus hkamentiensis é uma nova espécie extinta de lagarto que foi inesperadamente encontrada presa em âmbar birmanês. Ninguém esperava que um réptil inteiro fosse tão bem preservado, desde sua pele escamosa até seu esqueleto.

O que são agora os olhos vazios do Retinosaurus pode ter visto dinossauros ou samambaias gigantes ou libélulas do tamanho de sua cabeça. Foi determinado que era um jovem que se deparou com uma situação complicada quando se deparou com uma bola de âmbar de árvore da qual não conseguiu escapar. Estava tão bem preservado que o paleontólogo Andrej Čerňanský da Universidade Comenius e sua equipe, que recentemente publicou um estudo na Scientific Reports , abordaram o lagarto pré-histórico quase como se estivesse vivo

“Conseguimos estudar não apenas um esqueleto, mas até a aparência externa (escalada) do lagarto”, disse Čerňanský ao SYFY WIRE. "Na verdade, podemos estudar o animal da mesma forma que os herpetologistas estudam as espécies modernas."

O retinossauro não é um dinossauro (“saurus” na verdade significa “lagarto”), mas ainda uma relíquia fascinante de uma era perdida.

caption:
#SelfieSunday I have definitely underestimated the power of self-care. I don’t mean working out or keeping up with school and work…. The little things: taking a bath and reading a chapter of a new book; doing a bit of makeup and updating your hair; hell, even just taking the time to shave properly and take time to apply lotion and put on clothes you enjoy even if there is no place to go. Those. When did I forget about those?  When did I start to avoid wearing certain clothes that I know I love just because I’m not happy that I’ve gained a bit of weight?
.
*
After two of the hardest weeks mentally, I finally found, connected the dots, and learned what I needed to get better. This one isn’t a switch that quickly flipped but took reflection and planning. Learning my thought processes and what I need. This past week has been better. Maybe not leaps and bounds better but I learned who I need to see and socialize with to be happy and the best way to manage not only my stress but my response to stress around me. 
.
*
So here’s to the start of a new week where I continue to heal and keep my thoughts and priorities straight. And to continue to get back to feeling like me again. 
.
*

caption:
#광고 #협찬 #제품제공 

💛필요한 것만 심플하게 #엘러브 💛

얼마 전에 엘러브에서 ‘듀얼앰플크림 너리싱케어 라이트’를 보내주셔서 사용해보게 되었습니다☺️

이 제품은 받기 전부터 세계적인 5성급 호텔 <포시즌스호텔서울> 스파에 입점되어있고 실제 스파 테라피 관리에서도 사용이 되고 있는 데다 듀얼 용기라서 얼마나 편하고 제품이 좋을까 기대를 많이 하고 있었습니다! 그리고 역시나 받아서 사용해 보니 한 제품에 모든 것이 다 들어있어 편리하고 제품 또한 좋아서 너무 만족스러웠습니다✨

상단은 앰플, 하단은 크림으로 구성되어있어요
앰플과 크림 모두 피부에 자극이 없이 편했고 흡수력과 보습력이 만족스러웠습니다!

앰플은 우선 향이 강하지 않고 은은하게 올라와서 너무 마음에 들었습니다 양도 넉넉해서 하나로 스킨케어하기에 충분했습니다!

💛 앰플오일
✔피부 진정 및 보호 효능이 있는 동백나무씨오일 
✔️각질 및 노폐물 제거에 도움을 주는 사과씨오일
✔️끈적임 없이 빠르게 흡수되는 워터리 오일 제형
✔️無향료성분, 친환경 프리미엄 식물성 캡슐

보습크림은 제형이 푸딩 같아서 바르기 전부터 기분이 몽글몽글 좋았어요! 향도 강하지 않고 잘 펴 바를 수 있어서 마음에 들었어요😁 흡수력도 뛰어났고 무엇보다 촉촉해서 건성인 제 피부가 부드러워지는게 느껴져 만족스러웠습니당

💛 보습크림
✔️판테놀, 동백나무꽃추출물, 발효올리브오일 함유
✔️미백/주름개선 이중기능성 화장품
✔️외부 환경에 지친 피부 진정
✔️탄탄하고 생기있는 피부

Katsucon 2022 is all done. I worked my event and then spent the rest of my time in my room. My Judges and staff were wonderful, and I could not ask for a better group of people to work with. I also stopped at the MGM National Harbor and checked out their Lunar New Years decorations, which has been a katsu tradition since the MGM opened up. Now I am going to go sleep forever, do laundry and pet my cats.

caption:
*MENTAL HEALTH*

i wanted to share this. Btw I hate this picture so much on the left! 🤦

The picture on the left is after a shoulder operation I had done a few years ago. I had a inch wide hole In the back of my shoulder with a big cyst developing behind it and partial tear to my bicep tendon. The recovery for this were up to 6months to 2years. They told me it looked like I had dislocated my shoulder 6/7 times 🤦. They put 4 stiches around my ball and socket joint to hold it in. They told I wouldn't be able to do certain exercises again, would never have certain movement again and to keep away from any kind of heavy lifting.

Honestly this whole experience were overwhelming. 3 month after my operation I had lost 3/4 stone. I looked like I hadnt trained before. I couldn't wash myself or dress myself. All my independence were gone. I were lucky to have the right people round me and helped me get through this.

The right picture is me now. This picture tells you I did everything that the hospital siad I couldn't do and more and now my shoulder is stronger than ever. 

If I didn't have the right people around and the right mindset. My mental health would have deteriated and I would of never made a full recovery. 🌠

caption:
Throwback: How facial hair affected me. 

My #Insecurity: Since the day I noticed the hair on my neck, I knew from that point on, I would have issues. I already had an excessive spread of hair on my bikini line, armpit hair grew fast, a extra hairy trail line, and now it was neck hair. I felt like things couldn't get worse until I noticed the hair on my jawline, around my chin, and some cross between sideburns and jawline started to grow over time with age. Don't let it stop there! The dark spots/hyperpigmentation seem to never fade, making it the icing on the cake. How the hell was I going to be able to hide all this mess and still feel comfortable with myself? I started dealing with this in my teen years, where that was the time to think about your looks the most. 

My #Embarassment : Trying to hide the fact that I was indeed a hairy face woman was hard. I know most of us can relate when we joke about growing a beard, because it's real-life for us. I never looked at any makeup tutorials to hide my imperfections, it was already hard to find a good foundation that matched my smudgy brown skin tone (at the time). I tried to blend what I found anyway. Turned out I just caused more attention to myself. I really noticed it was a problem when I was modeling, I could see the craziness through my close-up shots. I'd ask the photographers to work their magic and erase the nonsense that was clearly there. If I could see it through photos, what could people see in person? Plus, I was staining a lot the necklines on my tops. That had to stop. 

My #depression : In general I was somewhat an #introvert. I've always kept to myself, had a super small circle of friends, and building new relationships wasn't easy. Always feltblike I would be talked about or stared at. I didn't really put myself out there to date. I didn't want any guy getting too close to me to notice my flaws. Consciously choosing not to be apart of social gatherings was not at the top of my list. So I focused on my talents, worked on building a future through my studies, and I was pretty set on deciding that I would be one of those women married to their career.

caption:
📍Магний📍
Это тема слишком актуальная и часто задаваемая!
⠀
Дефицита магния, не такая уж это и редкость☝️. Восполнять можно с помощью дополнительного приёма препаратов магния, минеральных вод и продуктов с высоким содержанием Мg.

🥑Из продуктов:
Магний в больших количествах содержится в ламинарии, кунжуте, авокадо, семенах подсолнечника и тыквы, сое, орехах, пророщенных зернах пшеницы, зелени, фасоли, буром рисе, горохе, бананах, черносливе, финиках, чёрном шоколаде и некоторых других продуктах.
⠀
🧊Минеральная вода с высоким содержанием магния - Донат Mg.
Лучше принимать в тёплом виде, начиная с маленькой порции, 100 мл, постепенно увеличивая. Может давать слабительный эффект. При употреблении 2-3 стаканов в день удовлетворяет потребность организма в магнии.

✔Ну и непосредственно к самим ФОРМАМ МАГНИЯ.
⠀
▪️ МАЛАТ. Это магний с яблочной кислотой. Полезен при хронической усталости, болевых ощущениях в теле, сильных умственных нагрузках. Магний малат придаёт энергии и бодрит. Поэтому его следует принимать утром.
⠀
▪️ТАУРАТ. Это магний соединённый с таурином. Его хорошо принимать при заболеваниях сердечно-сосудистой системы.
⠀
▪️ ОРОТАТ. Это магний с оротовой кислотой. Также, как и таурат, хорошо принимать при сердечно-сосудистых заболеваниях.
⠀
▪️ТРЕОНАТ. Это магний с треонином. Эта форма магния самая подходящая для улучшения здоровья мозга, так как проникает через ГЭБ. Способствует улучшению памяти, когнитивных расстройств, депрессии и других проявлений заболеваний неврологического характера.
⠀
▪️ГЛИЦИНАТ. Это магний с глицином. Эта форма магния самая подходящая для быстрого успокоения, расслабления, снижения тревожности, симптомов ПМС, а также детоксикации.
⠀
▪️ЦИТРАТ. Магний в этой форме обладает мягким слабительным действием. Подходящая форма при заболеваниях почек.
⠀
▪️ АСПАРТАТ. Это магний с аспарагиновой кислотой. Имеет высокую биодоступность, используется при сердечно-сосудистых заболеваниях в калиево-магниевых комплексах. Однако высокие уровни аспарагиновой кислоты в мозгу являются нейротоксином и такая форма является не подходящей для многих людей.

caption:
🌿Monstera🌿
Plants R Friends
_____________________
Ich möchte euch die erste neue Bilderreihe aus meinen neuen Homestudio zeigen. Und meine Monstera war ein perfekter Shooting Partner dafür. 
Das kleine neue Arbeitszimmer, zum künstlerisch tätig werden, ist noch nicht fertig und meine Fotografen Ader brauchte dringend wieder was zu tun. Daher hab ich schon Mal getestet was möglich ist, was ich ändern muss und wie ich mit dem Platz auskomme. Mein damaliges Fotostudio war mehr als doppelt so groß früher. Mich da jetzt etwas einzuschränken war gar nicht so leicht. Ich kann jetzt jedenfalls schon einmal sagen, es ist so gut wie alles möglich tatsächlich 😬.

caption:
Um amor eterno
Existiam uma garota chamada Raquel de 16 anos e um garoto chamado Noah de 18 anos,eles se conheceram aleatoriamente por amigos comuns, porém eles não se davam muito bem,pois tinham pensamentos e comportamentos muito diferentes um do outro,mas o que nenhum dos dois sabiam é que eles eram predestinados a ficarem juntos.O tempo foi passando e eles deixaram as indiferenças de lado e acabaram virando melhores amigos, eles perceberam que tinham coisas em comum,a Raquel já estava gostando do Noah, porém ele só a via como melhor amiga, não sentia nada além disso,ele gostava mesmo era uma outra menina e Raquel acabou se afastando do Noah por conta disso, só que a conexão deles eram tão forte que eles não conseguiram ficar um longe do outro,a Raquel estava tentando esquece-lô,mas era muito difícil,o que ela não sabia é que o Noah também estava se apaixonando por ela, só que o Noah era um garoto muito complicado e confuso e quase nunca se declarava para as pessoas que ele gostava,o tempo foi passando e esse sentimento foi aumentando, certo dia o Noah resolveu se declarar para a Raquel e ela correspondeu os sentimentos dele e eles começaram a namorar,com tempo os dois estavam passando por muitas problemas familiares e a Raquel teve que se mudar de cidade,com a mudança da Raquel eles decidiram terminar. Desde que a Raquel foi embora o Noah não teve mais notícias dela,ele teve novos relacionamento,mas nunca conseguiu esquecer a Raquel. Passaram se 5 anos e eles acabaram se encontrando por um acaso e conversaram bastante até que decidiram retomar o relacionamento,passou uns 6 meses e o relacionamento estava indo super bem e o Noah decidiu pedir a Raquel em casamento,eles se casaram e tiveram 5 filhos dentre eles o Beijamin Gabriel,a Maya,a Emma,a Chloé e o Hidan e com seus filhos foram muito felizes.
